column21: Did you like the location at 9:15 + B? Where should we ask to be placed next year?
column22:
Helioz pulse! Where should we spend camp effort and resources?

If something went well, maybe we should invest more time on it: that's not a bad thing! 

In theory we could have spent too much effort on something important but also done a bad job of it: in that case please just mark it on the left, needing more effort scale and we will try to be more effective next year :)
